


########################################## 


set node_(0) [ $ns_  node 0 ] 
$node_(0) set sinkStatus_ 1 

$node_(0) set position_update_interval_ $opt(position_update_interval) 

$god_ new_node $node_(0) 
$node_(0) random-motion 0 
$node_(0) set X_ 500.000 
$node_(0) set Y_ 46000.000 
$node_(0) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(0) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(0) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(0) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(0) $a_(0)
 $a_(0) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(0) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(0) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(0) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(0) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(0) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(0) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(25) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(25) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(25) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(25) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(25) $a_(25)
 $a_(25) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(25) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(25) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(25) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(25) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(25) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(25) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(50) $a_(50)
 $a_(50) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(50) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(50) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(50) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(50) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(50) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(50) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(126) set position_update_interval_ $opt(position_update_interval) 

$god_ new_node $node_(126) 
$node_(126) random-motion 0 
$node_(126) set X_ 126500.000 
$node_(126) set Y_ 47000.000 
$node_(126) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(126) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(126) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(126) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(126) $a_(126)
 $a_(126) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(126) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(126) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(126) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(126) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(126) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(126) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes



##########################################

$node_(151) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(151) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(151) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(151) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(151) $a_(151)
 $a_(151) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(151) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(151) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(151) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(151) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(151) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(151) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

set a_(176) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(176) $a_(176)
 $a_(176) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(176) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(176) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(176) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(176) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(176) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(176) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

 $a_(201) cmd set-target-x -20

 $a_(201) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(201) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(227) set Z_ 500.000

$node_(252) set position_update_interval_ $opt(position_update_interval) 

$god_ new_node $node_(252) 
$node_(252) random-motion 0 
$node_(252) set X_ 252500.000 
$node_(252) set Y_ 48000.000 
$node_(252) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(252) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(252) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(252) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(252) $a_(252)
 $a_(252) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(252) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(252) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(252) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(252) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(252) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(252) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(277) set Y_ 48000.000 
$node_(277) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(277) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(277) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(277) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(277) $a_(277)
 $a_(277) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(277) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(277) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(277) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(277) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(277) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(277) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

set a_(302) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(302) $a_(302)
 $a_(302) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(302) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(302) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(302) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(302) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(302) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(302) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

 $a_(327) cmd set-target-x -20

 $a_(327) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(378) set sinkStatus_ 1 

$node_(378) set position_update_interval_ $opt(position_update_interval) 

$god_ new_node $node_(378) 
$node_(378) random-motion 0 
$node_(378) set X_ 378500.000 
$node_(378) set Y_ 49000.000 
$node_(378) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(378) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(378) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(378) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(378) $a_(378)
 $a_(378) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(378) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(378) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(378) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(378) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(378) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(378) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(403) set Y_ 50000.000 
$node_(403) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(403) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(403) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(403) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(403) $a_(403)
 $a_(403) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(403) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(403) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(403) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(403) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(403) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(403) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

set a_(428) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(428) $a_(428)
 $a_(428) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(428) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(428) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(428) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(428) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(428) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(428) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

 $a_(453) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(453) cmd set-target-y -10

 $a_(453) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(453) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(504) set position_update_interval_ $opt(position_update_interval) 

$god_ new_node $node_(504) 
$node_(504) random-motion 0 
$node_(504) set X_ 504500.000 
$node_(504) set Y_ 51000.000 
$node_(504) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(504) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(504) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(504) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(504) $a_(504)
 $a_(504) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(504) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(504) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(504) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(504) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(504) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(504) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(529) set Z_ 500.000

 $a_(529) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(529) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(529) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(529) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(529) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(529) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(529) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(554) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(554) $a_(554)
 $a_(554) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(554) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(554) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(554) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(554) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(554) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(554) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(579) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(579) $a_(579)
 $a_(579) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(579) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(579) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(579) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(579) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(579) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(579) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(604) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(604) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(604) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(604) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(604) $a_(604)
 $a_(604) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(604) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(604) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(604) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(604) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(604) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(604) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(629) set Z_ 500.000

 $a_(629) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(629) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(629) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(629) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(629) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(629) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(629) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

 $a_(679) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(679) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(679) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(679) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(679) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(679) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(679) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(704) $a_(704)
 $a_(704) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(704) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(704) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(704) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(704) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(704) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(704) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

set rt [$node_(729) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(729) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(729) $a_(729)
 $a_(729) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(729) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(729) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(729) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(729) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(729) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(729) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

 $a_(778) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(778) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(778) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(778) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(778) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(778) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(778) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(803) set Y_ 54000.000 
$node_(803) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(803) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(803) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(803) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(803) $a_(803)
 $a_(803) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(803) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(803) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(803) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(803) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(803) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(803) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(852) set X_ 852500.000 
$node_(852) set Y_ 54000.000 
$node_(852) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(852) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(852) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(852) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(852) $a_(852)
 $a_(852) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(852) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(852) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(852) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(852) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(852) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(852) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(877) set sinkStatus_ 1 

$node_(877) set position_update_interval_ $opt(position_update_interval) 

$god_ new_node $node_(877) 
$node_(877) random-motion 0 
$node_(877) set X_ 877500.000 
$node_(877) set Y_ 54000.000 
$node_(877) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(877) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(877) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(877) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(877) $a_(877)
 $a_(877) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(877) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(877) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(877) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(877) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(877) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(877) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

 $a_(926) cmd set-range $opt(range)

$node_(950) set X_ 950500.000 
$node_(950) set Y_ 55000.000 
$node_(950) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(950) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(950) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(950) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(950) $a_(950)
 $a_(950) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(950) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(950) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(950) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(950) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(950) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(950) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(999) set X_ 999500.000 
$node_(999) set Y_ 55000.000 
$node_(999) set Z_ 500.000 
$node_(999) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(999) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(999) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(999) $a_(999)
 $a_(999) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(999) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(999) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(999) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

 $a_(999) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(999) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-x -20

 $a_(999) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(999) cmd set-range $opt(range)

$node_(1699) set X_ 699500.000 
$node_(1699) set Y_ 52000.000 
$node_(1699) set Z_ 1500.000 
$node_(999) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(999) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(999) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(999) $a_(999)
 $a_(999) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(999) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(999) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(999) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(999) set position_update_interval_ $opt(position_update_interval) 

$god_ new_node $node_(999) 
$node_(999) random-motion 0 
$node_(1749) set X_ 749500.000 
$node_(1749) set Y_ 53000.000 
$node_(1749) set Z_ 1500.000 
$node_(999) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(999) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(999) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(999) $a_(999)
 $a_(999) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(999) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(999) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(999) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(999) set sinkStatus_ 1 

$node_(999) set position_update_interval_ $opt(position_update_interval) 

$god_ new_node $node_(999) 
$node_(999) random-motion 0 
$node_(1774) set X_ 774500.000 
$node_(1774) set Y_ 53000.000 
$node_(1774) set Z_ 1500.000 
$node_(999) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(999) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(999) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(999) $a_(999)
 $a_(999) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(999) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(999) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(999) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(999) set sinkStatus_ 1 

$node_(999) set position_update_interval_ $opt(position_update_interval) 

$god_ new_node $node_(999) 
$node_(999) random-motion 0 
$node_(1974) set X_ 974500.000 
$node_(1974) set Y_ 55000.000 
$node_(1974) set Z_ 1500.000 
$node_(999) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(999) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(999) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(999) $a_(999)
 $a_(999) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(999) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(999) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(999) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes

$node_(999) random-motion 0 
$node_(1999) set X_ 999500.000 
$node_(1999) set Y_ 55000.000 
$node_(1999) set Z_ 1500.000 
$node_(999) set passive 1 


set rt [$node_(999) set ragent_] 
$rt set control_packet_size  $opt(routing_control_packet_size)  

set a_(999) [new Agent/UWSink] 
 $ns_ attach-agent $node_(999) $a_(999)
 $a_(999) attach-vectorbasedforward $opt(width)
 $a_(999) cmd set-range $opt(range) 
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-x -20
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-y -10
 $a_(999) cmd set-target-z -20
 $a_(999) cmd set-filename $opt(datafile)
 $a_(999) cmd set-packetsize $opt(packet_size) ;# # of bytes
